<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Drowsy" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Drowsy,</orth> sleepy, heavy, dull: <cit><quote>sleep when I am d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 1.3.17" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado I, 3, 17</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. jn 3.4.109" default="NO" valid="yes">John III, 4, 109</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 5.3.228" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 V, 3, 228</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 4.1.96" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. IV, 1, 96</bibl>. <cit><quote>dapples the d. east with spots of grey,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 5.3.27" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado V, 3, 27</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. h5 4.0" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV Chor.</bibl> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.0" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV Chor.</bibl> <cit><quote>the d. race of night,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jn 3.3.39" default="NO" valid="yes">John III, 3, 39</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.1.5" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B IV, 1, 5</bibl>. <cit><quote>from their d. beds,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.2.23" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 2, 23</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>by the dead and d. fire,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.399" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. V, 399</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>d. hums,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 3.2.42" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. III, 2, 42</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>make heaven d. with the harmony,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 4.3.345" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL IV, 3, 345</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>puts the d. and neglected act freshly on me,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 1.2.174" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. I, 2, 174</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the organs break up their d. grave,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.1.22" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 1, 22</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>their d. spirits,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 2.2.210" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. II, 2, 210</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tro 5.5.32" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 5, 32</bibl>. <cit><quote>all the d. syrups of the world,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 3.3.331" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. III, 3, 331</bibl></cit> (== disposing to sleep).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>